com.stormpath.sdk.oauth

Interface OauthGrantAuthenticationResult

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Oauth2AuthenticationResult

    public interface OauthGrantAuthenticationResult
extends Oauth2AuthenticationResult
    Contains the resultant AccessToken and all its related properties after a successful Grant Authentication request.
    Since:
    1.0.RC7
    See Also:
    Oauth2Authenticator.authenticate(Oauth2AuthenticationRequest), Oauth2Authenticator.authenticate(Oauth2AuthenticationRequest)
